- Bye.

1426
01:42:44,431 --> 01:42:45,463
Rama.

1427
01:42:49,681 --> 01:42:51,660
Let's go. Come on.

1428
01:43:45,921 --> 01:43:47,754
Shall we go?

1429
01:43:59,306 --> 01:44:01,171
Come, son. Let's go.

1430
01:44:54,848 --> 01:44:57,244
Hello. Welcome home!

1431
01:46:48,504 --> 01:46:51,973
Look...

1432
01:46:52,285 --> 01:46:56,410
