1437
01:48:19,421 --> 01:48:21,567
It's been over a year...

1438
01:48:21,921 --> 01:48:23,379
It's hard to believe.

1439
01:48:24,181 --> 01:48:33,254
So cheerful... so full of life...

1440
01:48:34,546 --> 01:48:37,046
